test.support.import_module¶

test.support.import_module(name, deprecated=False, *, required_on=())¶

Import and return the module to be tested, raising SkipTest if it is not available.

If deprecated is True, any module or package deprecation messages will be suppressed. If a module is required on a platform but optional for others, set required_on to an iterable of platform prefixes which will be compared against sys.platform.
